rows.label: qst106004_msg0001
rows.name: Dad, I've brought the materials, mo!

rows.label: qst106004_msg0002
rows.name:
Welcome back, Tora, mo. The
workshop is ready, mo.

rows.label: qst106004_msg0003
rows.name:
I'll make the expansion
parts, so Kiku, make sure
no one interrupts, mo.

rows.label: qst106004_msg0004
rows.name:
Yes, you can count on
me, Masterpon, mo.

rows.label: qst106004_msg0005
rows.name:
Um... if Hana-chan is going
to be an adult, she'll need
to change her clothes, right?

rows.label: qst106004_msg0006
rows.name: Really? Isn't her current outfit fine?

rows.label: qst106004_msg0007
rows.name:
No, if her physique changes,
that won't work, right?

rows.label: qst106004_msg0008
rows.name:
If she gets bigger in her current
clothes, that would be a problem.

rows.label: qst106004_msg0009
rows.name: Exactly!

rows.label: qst106004_msg0010
rows.name:
Besides, wouldn't it be sad if she
were naked after the modification?

rows.label: qst106004_msg0011
rows.name: Is that so, mo?

rows.label: qst106004_msg0012
rows.name:
Hikari and Homura have quite
the outfits, mo. Hana is a
Blade, so Hana doesn't mind, mo.

rows.label: qst106004_msg0013
rows.name: No! Absolutely not!

rows.label: qst106004_msg0014
rows.name: Hana-chan needs to have more modesty.

rows.label: qst106004_msg0015
rows.name: Hmm, I don't really understand, mo...

rows.label: qst106004_msg0016
rows.name:
But a new outfit would
definitely give off more
of a powered-up feel, mo!

rows.label: qst106004_msg0017
rows.name:
That would make for a more
exciting development, mo!

rows.label: qst106004_msg0018
rows.name:
Then, this Kiku will make a
new outfit for my sister, mo.

rows.label: qst106004_msg0019
rows.name:
Nee-sama is going to make
me a new outfit, mo?

rows.label: qst106004_msg0020
rows.name:
Yes, for my cute little sister,
mo. I will do my best, mo.

rows.label: qst106004_msg0021
rows.name:
Then, since Hana will be
very adult, I'd like a
sexy outfit, please, mo.

rows.label: qst106004_msg0022
rows.name:
And a design that hints
at her cuteness...mo...

rows.label: qst106004_msg0023
rows.name:
Furthermore, I'd like a design
that feels strong and cool, mo.

rows.label: qst106004_msg0024
rows.name:
Mo-mo, that's quite a
lot of requests, mo...

rows.label: qst106004_msg0025
rows.name:
That's a bit too much to
ask for, isn't it...

rows.label: qst106004_msg0026
rows.name: Is it impossible, mo?

rows.label: qst106004_msg0027
rows.name:
No, for my sister's sake,
mo. As her older sister, I
will see it through, mo!

rows.label: qst106004_msg0028
rows.name: Thank you, Nee-sama, mo!

rows.label: qst106004_msg0029
rows.name:
But it seems I'll need additional
materials to make the outfit, mo.

rows.label: qst106004_msg0030
rows.name: What do you need?

rows.label: qst106004_msg0031
rows.name: Cubic Diamonds, Ambler Stigmas...

rows.label: qst106004_msg0032
rows.name:
...and Genbu-Weave Broadcloth
would be good, mo.

rows.label: qst106004_msg0033
rows.name: I see, understood. Hana-chan, let's go!

rows.label: qst106004_msg0034
rows.name:
Roger, mo! Hana will get
the best materials, mo!
